{"tid":36150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星期三，松泰就知有冇得做議員？飯民會背後開槍嗎？","createTime":"2016-12-12T13:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T10:45:45.000Z","uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32f5b56df7669677ace0621bce263dba5796a01a","tid":36150,"uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"立法會秘書處今日（12月12日）發出通告，指本星期三（12月14日）舉行的大會上，將辯論一項根據《議事規則》第49B（1A）條動議的議案，該項議案由謝偉俊提出，內容為：「鑑於鄭松泰議員行為不檢，本會根據《基本法》第七十九（七）條對其作出譴責。」 議程指在10月19日的立法會會議，熱血公民鄭松泰在主席宣布點算法定人數及所有民建聯議員不在席時，將他們擺放在桌上的國旗及區旗展示品倒轉擺放，認為有關舉動屬行為不檢，故提出譴責動議。 預料有關議案將會在本周會期內表決，如議案獲在席會議的人數超過3份之2贊成通過，鄭松泰的議席便會被剝奪。 鄭松泰將會明日下午2時半開記招，再回應有關事宜。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-12-2016/34498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F12-12-2016%2F34498&d=KvtloBbkJC6H0RGqyDvczEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=4a7da516\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-12-2016/34498</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2016"},{"pid":"f5bed82be97f22f87c6417704efe148a95266cfd","tid":36150,"uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:41:08.000Z","msg":"唉<br />\n<br />\n城邦派唯一生還者"},{"pid":"b5fc562229c5dcc23efc2163325ff69d6a6a2733","tid":36150,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:43:15.000Z","msg":"佢都冇埋本土派今鋪就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc20ffe4f83a38da6a1675125267baea5b44cf3f","tid":36150,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:46:49.000Z","msg":"泛民發圍啦"},{"pid":"891b97ebeb0566fcd6bd2a9296c8a60690ae0351","tid":36150,"uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:13:06.000Z","msg":"飯團私怨太過天"},{"pid":"30a47444832a7f6a74c1b84c4b26a75ad5b1ad7c","tid":36150,"uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep